<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Contrail Impact Predictor</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sora:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css"/>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js"></script>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  :root {
    --bg: #0b1117;
    --bg2: #17222e;
    --ink: #e6edf4;
    --ink2: #b8c3cf;
    --ink3: #5d738a;
    --high: #c96b3b;
    --med: #d2a14d;
    --low: #5e9b93;
    --high-light: #fce8e4;
    --med-light: #fdf0e0;
    --low-light: #e4f2ea;
    --white: #faf8f5;
    --sans: 'Sora', sans-serif;
    --mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  html, body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--ink); font-family: var(--sans); min-height: 100vh; }
  body { opacity: 0; animation: fadeIn 0.6s ease forwards; }
  @keyframes fadeIn { to { opacity: 1; } }

body::before {
content:'';
position:fixed;
inset:0;
pointer-events:none;
background:
radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), transparent 30%),
radial-gradient(circle at 80% 40%, rgba(255,255,255,0.03), transparent 40%),
radial-gradient(circle at 50% 80%, rgba(255,255,255,0.04), transparent 35%);
mix-blend-mode: screen;
opacity: .55;
}


  /* HERO */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr auto;
    padding: 0;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
  }

  .hero-nav {
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.15);
    position: relative; z-index: 10;
  }
  .nav-logo { font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .nav-date { font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); }

  .hero-center {
    display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
    padding: 60px 40px;
    position: relative; z-index: 10;
  }

  .hero-eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2);
    letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px;
  }
  .eyebrow-line { width: 40px; height: 1px; background: var(--ink2); }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(56px, 9vw, 120px);
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 0.9;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }
  .hero-title em { font-style: normal; color: var(--high); }

  .hero-bottom {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.15);
    position: relative; z-index: 10;
  }
  .hero-stat {
    padding: 28px 40px;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.15);
  }
  .hero-stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .hs-num {
    font-size: 52px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: -0.04em; margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .hs-label { font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; }

  /* BIG CIRCLE BG */
  .hero-circle {
    position: absolute;
    width: 70vw; height: 70vw;
    max-width: 800px; max-height: 800px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.08);
    right: -20vw; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .hero-circle-2 {
    position: absolute;
    width: 50vw; height: 50vw;
    max-width: 600px; max-height: 600px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.05);
    right: -10vw; top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  /* SECTIONS */
  .section { padding: 80px 40px; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink); }
  .section-label {
    font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2);
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
  }
  .section-label::before { content: ''; display: block; width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--ink2); }

  /* CONDITIONS */
  .conditions-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 0; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  }
  .cond-box {
    padding: 32px; border-right: 2px solid var(--ink);
    position: relative; overflow: hidden;
  }
  .cond-box:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .cb-region { font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .cb-num { font-size: 64px; font-weight: 800; line-height: 1; letter-spacing: -0.04em; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .cb-unit { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; color: var(--ink2); margin-left: 4px; }
  .cb-label { font-size: 12px; color: var(--ink2); font-family: var(--mono); }
  .cb-risk {
    position: absolute; top: 32px; right: 32px;
    font-size: 10px; font-weight: 700; font-family: var(--mono);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 10px;
  }

  /* MAP SECTION */
  .map-section { padding: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink); }
  .map-header {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .mh-left {
    padding: 40px; border-right: 2px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .mh-title { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .mh-desc { font-size: 14px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 400px; }
  .mh-right { padding: 40px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: space-between; }
  .map-legend { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
  .ml-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .ml-bar { height: 3px; flex: 1; border-radius: 1px; }
  .ml-label { font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); width: 60px; text-align: right; }
  .ml-count { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; width: 40px; }

  #map { height: 460px; border-radius: 10px; }
  .leaflet-container { background: var(--bg2) !important; }

  /* FLIGHT PANEL */
  .flight-section {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 400px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
    min-height: 600px;
  }
  .flight-list-col { border-right: 2px solid var(--ink); overflow: hidden; }
  .fl-header {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    padding: 16px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.15);
    font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2);
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    background: var(--bg2);
  }
  .flight-scroll { max-height: 540px; overflow-y: auto; }
  .flight-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 3px; }
  .flight-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: var(--ink3); }
  .fl-row {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    padding: 14px 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.08);
    cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.1s; align-items: center;
  }
  .fl-row:hover { background: var(--bg2); }
  .fl-row.active { background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); }
  .fl-row.active .fl-airline { color: rgba(240,237,232,0.6); }
  .fl-callsign { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  .fl-airline { font-size: 11px; color: var(--ink2); margin-top: 2px; }
  .fl-val { font-size: 12px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); }
  .fl-row.active .fl-val { color: rgba(240,237,232,0.6); }
  .risk-pill {
    font-size: 9px; font-weight: 700; font-family: var(--mono);
    padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 10px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .rh { background: var(--high-light); color: var(--high); }
  .rm { background: var(--med-light); color: var(--med); }
  .rl { background: var(--low-light); color: var(--low); }
  .fl-row.active .rh { background: rgba(200,52,26,0.3); color: #ff8870; }
  .fl-row.active .rm { background: rgba(200,122,26,0.3); color: #ffbc70; }
  .fl-row.active .rl { background: rgba(26,122,60,0.3); color: #70e898; }

  /* DETAIL PANEL */
  .detail-col { padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .detail-empty {
    flex: 1; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    padding: 40px; text-align: center;
  }
  .de-hint { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink3); line-height: 1.7; }
  .detail-content { display: none; flex-direction: column; height: 100%; }
  .detail-content.visible { display: flex; }
  .dc-top { padding: 32px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.12); }
  .dc-callsign { font-size: 48px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.04em; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .dc-airline { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink2); margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .dc-risk-block { padding: 16px 20px; margin-bottom: 0; }
  .dcr-label { font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 4px; opacity: 0.7; }
  .dcr-val { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .dc-stats { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; border-top: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.12); }
  .dcs { padding: 20px 24px; border-right: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.12); border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.12); }
  .dcs:nth-child(even) { border-right: none; }
  .dcs-label { font-size: 9px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .dcs-val { font-size: 20px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
  .dc-suggestion { padding: 24px; flex: 1; background: var(--bg2); }
  .dcs-head { font-size: 10px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.1em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .dcs-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.75; }
  .dcs-body strong { color: var(--ink); font-weight: 600; }
  .dcs-body .action { color: var(--high); font-weight: 600; }
  .dcs-body .good { color: var(--low); font-weight: 600; }

  /* ABOUT */
  .about-section {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
  }
  .about-col { padding: 56px 40px; border-right: 2px solid var(--ink); }
  .about-col:last-child { border-right: none; }
  .ac-num { font-size: 72px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.05em; line-height: 1; color: var(--ink3); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .ac-title { font-size: 18px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .ac-body { font-size: 13px; color: var(--ink2); line-height: 1.75; }

  /* FOOTER */
  .footer {
    padding: 24px 40px;
    display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
  }
  .footer-left { font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink2); }
  .footer-right { font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--ink3); }

  /* FILTERS */
  .filter-row {
    display: flex; gap: 0; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink);
    overflow-x: auto;
  }
  .ftab {
    padding: 14px 24px; font-size: 11px; font-family: var(--mono);
    cursor: pointer; border-right: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.15);
    color: var(--ink2); transition: all 0.12s; white-space: nowrap;
    text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  .ftab:hover { background: var(--bg2); color: var(--ink); }
  .ftab.active { background: var(--ink); color: var(--bg); }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title { font-size: 48px; }
    .hero-bottom { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .hero-stat { border-right: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15,14,12,0.15); }
    .conditions-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .cond-box { border-right: none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink); }
    .map-header { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .mh-left { border-right: none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink); }
    .flight-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .flight-list-col { border-right: none; }
    .about-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .about-col { border-right: none; border-bottom: 2px solid var(--ink); }
    .hero-nav, .section, .map-section { padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-circle"></div>
  <div class="hero-circle-2"></div>

  <nav class="hero-nav">
    <div class="nav-logo">Contrail Impact Predictor</div>
    <div class="nav-date">UK Airspace</div>
  </nav>

  <div class="hero-center">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">
      <span class="eyebrow-line"></span>
      Aviation's invisible climate problem
    </div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Every flight<br>
      leaves a <em>mark</em><br>
      on the sky.
    </h1>
  </div>

  <div class="hero-bottom">
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="hs-num" id="h-total">42</div>
      <div class="hs-label">Flights tracked</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="hs-num" style="color:var(--high)" id="h-high">0</div>
      <div class="hs-label">High contrail risk</div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-stat">
      <div class="hs-num" style="color:var(--low)" id="h-low">0</div>
      <div class="hs-label">Low risk — contrails dissolve</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CONDITIONS -->
<section class="section">
  <div class="section-label">Atmospheric conditions · 250hPa cruise altitude</div>
  <div class="conditions-grid">
    <div class="cond-box" style="background:var(--med-light)">
      <div class="cb-region">South UK · London area</div>
      <div class="cb-num" style="color:#1f2730">−50<span class="cb-unit" style="color:#4a5560">°C</span></div>
      <div class="cb-label" style="color:#4a5560">64% relative humidity</div>
      <div class="cb-risk" style="background:var(--med-light);color:var(--med);border:1px solid var(--med)">Medium risk</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cond-box" style="background:var(--low-light)">
      <div class="cb-region">North UK · Manchester area</div>
      <div class="cb-num" style="color:#1f2730">−47<span class="cb-unit" style="color:#4a5560">°C</span></div>
      <div class="cb-label" style="color:#4a5560">40% relative humidity</div>
      <div class="cb-risk" style="background:var(--low-light);color:var(--low);border:1px solid var(--low)">Low risk</div>
    </div>
    <div class="cond-box" style="background:var(--bg)">
      <div class="cb-region">Key insight</div>
      <div class="cb-num" style="color:var(--ink);font-size:36px;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.02em">Same<br>altitude.<br>Different<br>impact.</div>
      <div class="cb-label" style="margin-top:12px">Location determines contrail formation, not just height.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MAP -->
<section class="map-section">
  <div class="map-header">
    <div class="mh-left">
      <div class="mh-title">42 flights.<br>Real positions.<br>Real risk.</div>
      <div class="mh-desc">Each dot represents a real flight captured via ADS-B transponder signals. Colour indicates individual contrail risk calculated from actual atmospheric data at that exact location.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="mh-right">
      <div class="section-label" style="margin-bottom:24px">Risk legend</div>
      <div class="map-legend">
        <div class="ml-row">
          <div class="ml-count" style="color:var(--high)" id="map-high">0</div>
          <div class="ml-bar" style="background:var(--high)"></div>
          <div class="ml-label" style="color:var(--high)">HIGH</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-row">
          <div class="ml-count" style="color:var(--med)" id="map-med">0</div>
          <div class="ml-bar" style="background:var(--med)"></div>
          <div class="ml-label" style="color:var(--med)">MEDIUM</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ml-row">
          <div class="ml-count" style="color:var(--low)" id="map-low">0</div>
          <div class="ml-bar" style="background:var(--low)"></div>
          <div class="ml-label" style="color:var(--low)">LOW</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div id="map"></div>
</section>

<!-- FILTERS + FLIGHT LIST -->
<div class="filter-row">
  <div class="ftab active" onclick="filterFlights('ALL', this)">All flights</div>
  <div class="ftab" onclick="filterFlights('HIGH', this)" style="color:var(--high)">High risk</div>
  <div class="ftab" onclick="filterFlights('MEDIUM', this)" style="color:var(--med)">Medium risk</div>
  <div class="ftab" onclick="filterFlights('LOW', this)" style="color:var(--low)">Low risk</div>
  <div class="ftab" onclick="filterFlights('SOUTH', this)">South UK</div>
  <div class="ftab" onclick="filterFlights('NORTH', this)">North UK</div>
</div>

<div class="flight-section">
  <div class="flight-list-col">
    <div class="fl-header">
      <span>Flight</span><span>Alt</span><span>Temp</span><span>Humid</span><span>Risk</span>
    </div>
    <div class="flight-scroll" id="flightList"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="detail-col">
    <div class="detail-empty" id="detailEmpty">
      <div class="de-hint">Select a flight from the list or click a dot on the map to see its individual contrail risk assessment and routing recommendation.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="detail-content" id="detailContent">
      <div class="dc-top">
        <div class="dc-callsign" id="dc-callsign">—</div>
        <div class="dc-airline" id="dc-airline">—</div>
        <div class="dc-risk-block" id="dc-risk-block">
          <div class="dcr-label">Contrail risk</div>
          <div class="dcr-val" id="dc-risk-val">—</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-stats">
        <div class="dcs"><div class="dcs-label">Altitude</div><div class="dcs-val" id="dc-alt">—</div></div>
        <div class="dcs"><div class="dcs-label">Temperature</div><div class="dcs-val" id="dc-temp">—</div></div>
        <div class="dcs"><div class="dcs-label">Humidity</div><div class="dcs-val" id="dc-humid">—</div></div>
        <div class="dcs"><div class="dcs-label">Region</div><div class="dcs-val" id="dc-region">—</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="dc-suggestion">
        <div class="dcs-head">Routing recommendation</div>
        <div class="dcs-body" id="dc-suggestion">—</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ABOUT -->
<section class="about-section">
  <div class="about-col">
    <div class="ac-num">01</div>
    <div class="ac-title">What are contrails?</div>
    <div class="ac-body">Contrails are ice crystal trails left by aircraft engines at cruise altitude. In certain atmospheric conditions they persist for hours and spread into cirrus cloud — trapping heat and warming the climate well beyond the CO₂ from fuel alone. Some studies suggest contrails cause as much warming as all of aviation's CO₂ combined.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-col">
    <div class="ac-num">02</div>
    <div class="ac-title">Why location matters</div>
    <div class="ac-body">Today's data shows a striking contrast — flights over Manchester at 27–40% humidity create contrails that dissolve instantly. Identical flights at the same altitude over London at 60–78% humidity leave persistent trails for hours. Same altitude. Very different climate impact. This is what makes contrail avoidance operationally possible.</div>
  </div>
  <div class="about-col">
    <div class="ac-num">03</div>
    <div class="ac-title">The routing solution</div>
    <div class="ac-body">Airlines including British Airways and Lufthansa are actively trialling contrail avoidance routing. Small altitude adjustments of 2,000–4,000ft can move a flight out of ice-supersaturated layers entirely. This tool identifies in real time which flights would benefit most — the same decision-support logic used in live operational trials.</div>
  </div>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  <div class="footer-left">OpenSky Network ADS-B · Open-Meteo atmospheric API</div>
  <div class="footer-right">Contrail Impact Predictor · Svetlana</div>
</footer>

<script>
const FLIGHTS = [
  { callsign:'NSZ5700', airline:'Norwegian',             alt:10972, temp:-50.0, humid:60, lat:51.5144, lon:0.0587,  region:'SOUTH' },
  { callsign:'T7IRL',   airline:'Private',               alt:9227,  temp:-49.5, humid:58, lat:50.3051, lon:0.0892,  region:'SOUTH' },
  { callsign:'JNJ976',  airline:'Private',               alt:13106, temp:-50.0, humid:73, lat:51.7763, lon:0.6851,  region:'SOUTH' },
  { callsign:'EZY15JL', airline:'easyJet',               alt:8488,  temp:-49.0, humid:53, lat:50.7489, lon:0.5356,  region:'SOUTH' },
  { callsign:'VVV211',  airline:'Unknown',               alt:8839,  temp:-49.5, humid:78, lat:50.8441, lon:-0.8462, region:'SOUTH' },
